title: Jacques.Tati.Short.Films
description:
Presented here are three Jacques Tati short films with subtitles in Swedish, Danish, Norwegian and Finnish.

* Soigne ton gauche / Tr&auml;na upp din v&auml;nsterkrok (1936) 
  http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0028275/   

* L' ecole des facteurs / Skolan f&ouml;r brevb&auml;rare (1947)
  http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0040019/  

* Cours du soir / Kv&auml;llskursen (1967)
